    ipv6-multicast: Fix memory leak in input path.
    
    Have to free the skb before returning if we fail
    the fib lookup.
    
    Signed-off-by: Ben Greear <greearb@candelatech.com>
    Signed-off-by: David S. Miller <davem@davemloft.net>

